name: AE2 Frequency Display
tagline: Displays AE2 P2P Frequencies in the Waila tooltip
body:
### AE2 Frequency Display
A small Minecraft mod that displays AE2 P2P Frequencies in the Waila tooltip

This mod requires [Applied Energistics 2](http://ae-mod.info/) and Minecraft 1.7.10

![Build status](https://travis-ci.org/fraenkelc/AE2FrequencyDisplay.svg)
